"title": "8665: praise, reasons for",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8665",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture treats praise as the natural response of believers to God's person and actions.</p>\n<h2>Praise is commanded of God's people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:32\">PSA 68:32</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:5\">REV 19:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:4\">PSA 30:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:6\">PSA 150:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:10\">ISA 42:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:9-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:9–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Praise is due to God alone</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:21\">DEU 10:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:25\">1CH 16:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">ISA 42:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:4\">PSA 66:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:15-Ps118:21\">PSA 118:15–118:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:13\">PSA 148:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Praise is pleasing to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30-Ps69:31\">PSA 69:30–69:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:3\">PSA 135:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:1\">PSA 147:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:20-Isa43:21\">ISA 43:20–43:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:10-Isa61:11\">ISA 61:10–61:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:11\">JER 13:11</a></p>\n<h2>Praise as an act of witness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:11\">PSA 9:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:50\">2SA 22:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:1-Ps34:3\">PSA 34:1–34:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:12\">ISA 42:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:13\">2CO 9:13</a></p>\n<h2>Praise in response to God's nature</h2>\n<h3>For his greatness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:3\">DEU 32:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:2\">PSA 150:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:25\">1CH 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:6\">NEH 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:1\">PSA 104:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:8\">MAT 9:8</a></p>\n<h3>For his righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:8-Ps98:9\">PSA 98:8–98:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:37\">DAN 4:37</a></p>\n<h3>For his faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:9-Ps57:10\">PSA 57:9–57:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:2\">PSA 138:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:15-1Kgs8:20\">1KI 8:15–8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:1\">PSA 89:1</a></p>\n<h3>For his strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:16\">PSA 59:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:7\">PSA 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:1\">PSA 81:1</a></p>\n<h2>Praise in response to God's deeds</h2>\n<h3>For deliverance from enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:10\">EXO 18:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:46-Ps18:48\">PSA 18:46–18:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:20\">GEN 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:24\">JDG 16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:1-Ps43:4\">PSA 43:1–43:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:1-Ps124:7\">PSA 124:1–124:7</a></p>\n<h3>For answered prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:6\">PSA 28:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:19-Ps66:20\">PSA 66:19–66:20</a></p>\n<h3>For sending his Son, Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:68-Luke1:69\">LUK 1:68–1:69</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3\">EPH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10-Luke2:14\">LUK 2:10–2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:28\">LUK 2:25–2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:53\">LUK 24:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:6\">1PE 1:3–1:6</a></p>",
